title: Mondays with Matt & J - A Pro Relationship Tip for Solving Disagreements
description:
Matt and J serve up some laughs and fun facts to get your Monday off to the right foot! Tune in to learn a few easy healthy alternatives to your favorite junk food, a pro-relationship tip for the next time you find yourself in an argument with your S/O, and a few unexpected run-ins the Dooley's had with nature...

Follow them on IG here:

instagram.com/mattjdooley

instagram.com/jordanleedooley
author: matt@jordanleedooley.com (Jordan Lee Dooley)
